[2026-03-09 16:59:03] [1d5c3289-82f5-47bd-941c-b7c9d068124c] CLAUDE: ## Review findings (main → HEAD)  ### Code Quality  1. **`src/bridge.ts:38,43`** — `console.debug` calls left from debugging. These should be removed before merging.    - **Fix**: Remove both `console.debug` lines.  ### Performance  2. **`src/bridge.ts:49`** — `[...text].slice(0, MAX_RUNES).join("")` allocates an array on every send. For short messages (the common case), the spread is unnecessary.    - **Fix**: Fast-path `if ([...text].length <= MAX_RUNES) return text` before truncating.  ### Test Coverage  3. **`src/bridge.test.ts`** — `markSeen` with a full-path ID is not tested. The test at line 87 uses `"msg-1"` which doesn't exercise `normalizeId`.    - **Fix**: Add a test: `markSeen("spaces/X/messages/123")` then `send("123", "text")` should be skipped.  ### Security / Documentation  No noteworthy issues. 
